{\pard \ql \sb240 \sa0 \sl0 \slmult1 \ilvl0 \li0 \lin0 \fi0 \ri0 \rin0 \s285 {\f1 \fs28 \lang1033 Tone values and other transcriptional conventions for the Ilan and H\'88\'6eb\'9e\'6e material are detailed in the References, beginning on p. {\field {\*\fldinst  PAGE }
